               <h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0">
                   <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">一、</span>
                   <span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span>
                   <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">账号相关</span>
               </h1>
               <p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0">
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">1</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何注销账号？</span>
               </p>
               <p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0">
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台暂不支持自主注销账号，若要注销，请邮件联系</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">【邮箱】</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">，或私信联系客服</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">【客服昵称】</span>
                   <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">2</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">绑定手机号时，提示手机号已被注册？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">绑定手机号显示手机号已注册，说明该手机号已注册过账号，若需要该手机号绑定其他账号，请用该手机号登录并前往账号设置内解绑手机号，然后再绑定现有账号。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q3</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">为什么无法登录账号？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">请根据登录失败提示检查原因，如不能解决，您可能是：</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、连续超过1年未登录的帐号，该帐号可能被系统收回，建议您定期保持帐号登录。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、由于违反用户协议规定，上传广告、涉黄涉爆、侵权等违法内容的用户，平台管理员会拉黑涉事帐号。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、如有其它紧急原因您可以发送邮件至：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">【邮箱】</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">二、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">相关</span></h1><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">4</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">上传了作品后，在首页或发现页找不到我的作品？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品需要进行平台审核通过后才能够公开至所有用户。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">首页展示顺序是通过算法决定的，新发布且平台认可的优质作品会得到更高的展示位置。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品审核的机制是什么？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">目前平台均为人工审核作品，以防违法、广告等信息污染平台环境。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">PS：目前均为人工审核，我们会尽快改进审核机制，达到发布5分钟内完成审核的速度标</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">准，敬请期待。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">6</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品审核需要多长时间？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">工作日（白天09:00至19:00）审核时间不超过2小时，节假日和晚间审核时间不超过24小时。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">7</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">可以编辑/删除我上传的作品吗？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">可以，但是参赛作品不允许删除哦。如需取消活动参与，请私信联系客服</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">【客服昵称】</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">三、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">平台推荐</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">相关</span></h1><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">8</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">平台推荐设计师有哪些特权？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">发布的作品更容易获得高展示位，获得更多曝光量</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台的征集作品活动、商业合作机会将优先获得消息与合作邀请</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何成为平台推荐设计师？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">在发布的作品数量达到5个时，平台会对创作者进行一次评定，评定结果将决定是否能够成为平台推荐设计师。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、评定维度：作品质量为主，作品类型、作品点赞率、评论率、商业合作性等为辅。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、平台会定期对创作者进行重新评定，视情况维持推荐或撤销推荐。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">10</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品推荐是什么？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台会定期或审核时，将最近的作品进行质量等级评定，优秀的作品会得到平台更高的首页展示位支持。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">11</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何获得作品推荐？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品质量高；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品完成度高；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品具有独特的表达手法；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品对其他的设计师有帮助，有启发，有激励</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">推荐作品还会以作者用心的程度、网友好评度等作为参考，客观推荐。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">四、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">赚钱必读指南</span></h1><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">12</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">什么是平台供稿人？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台供稿人是创作者与平台建立的一种【供稿→收购】的商业合作关系，旨在于为创作者提供一条可赚取高收益的道路。认证后创作者将于平台签订协议，在双方达成一致的前提下，平台通过征集形式购买创作者提供的供稿作品及其著作权。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">13</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">为什么要认证供稿人？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">因供稿作品的买卖，需双方签订协议才构成合法商业行为，故需要创作者提供相关个人/企业信息并认证后，创作者才有资格参与征集活动。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">PS：即使认证成为平台供稿人，你仍然拥有所上传作品著作权，只有当平台正式录用作品后，该作品的著作权才正式转为平台所有。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">14</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">什么是征集活动？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台会将设计需求以征集活动的形式发布在活动页列表，创作者可在活动页列表找寻自己有能力设计创作的活动，制作供稿作品参与活动，经平台认可的作品将会录用并支付相应报酬收益</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">15</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品入围有什么用？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品入围代表其已达到该活动要求的录用门槛，但入围并不保证百分百录用，创作者可加入活动群与活动运营咨询录用相关事宜。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、另一方面会将作品展示在活动的入围作品列表，为作品提供一定曝光度。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、非征集类活动的作品入围奖励，请以活动详情的说明为准。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">16</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：什么作品能够入围？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">征集类活动的作品入围评定维度：</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品符合活动说明的要求</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、作品质量、完成度达标</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、作品对后续参与的作品有教学意义、有启发</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">非征集类活动的作品入围标准，请以活动详情的说明为准。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">17</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：如何得知作品入围了？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品将会在平台</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">[</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">消息-通知</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">]</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">内发送作品入围通知</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">18</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何确定作品可被录用？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、若作品达到可以录用的标准后，活动运营将会通过私信、电话、QQ（默认私信）与创作者联系，沟通后续录用流程。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、作品入围后，建议创作者加入活动群（在活动详情内有公示），与活动运营咨询；若未达到录用标准，也可及时知晓未录用的原因进行作品调整，直至达到标准后录用。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">19</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何避免多次返工？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、请在参与活动进行作品制作前，详细阅读说明详情，按照规范进行作品设计。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、创作者可以参考已入围或已录用的作品，进一步理解设计方向与规范。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、开始设计前，请下载模板文件认真查看，并按照其规范进行设计。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4、建议创作者加入活动群，可了解其他创作者制作实况，也可与活动运营咨询与作品相关的疑问。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">20</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">录用报价的标准是什么？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">录用价格的评定标准维度：</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品质量、完成度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、符合活动要求的程度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、对活动要求理解能力、设计习惯（返工少）</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4、作品素材完成速度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">因活动所征集的作品素材类型不同，各类型的录用价格区间也会不同，但每个征集活动的录用价格区间均会公示至活动详情内。</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">21</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何提现？</span></p><p style="margin:10px auto; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">1、在</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">我的收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">页，即可找到提现入口，按流程操作完成后即可提交提现申请</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">2、平台每月15日-25日汇款当月的提现申请。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">3、若是个人提现，实际到账金额=提现金额-税费，税费按当月合计的提前额度计算。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">4、若是企业/机构提现，需寄送提现金额发票；请尽量保证平台在每月汇款期间内收到发票，若在此期间外收到，统一于下个月处理提现汇款。</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">
       </div>
    
